00:00:49,288 --> 00:00:53,751
3-ceg septembra 1973.
u 18:28 i 32 sekunde,

3
00:00:53,835 --> 00:00:59,006
plava muva sposobna da
mahne krilima 70 puta u minutu

4
00:00:59,131 --> 00:01:02,134
sletela je na ulicu St. Vincent
u Montmartru.

5
00:01:06,305 --> 00:01:10,184
U tom trenutku,
na terasi obliznjeg restorana,

6
00:01:10,309 --> 00:01:15,940
vetar je magijom ucinio da dve
case zaigraju, nevidjene na stolnjaku.

7
00:01:17,191 --> 00:01:21,946
U medjuvremenu, u stanu na 5-tom
spratu na Aveniji Trudaine, Pariz 9,

8
00:01:22,029 --> 00:01:26,784
vracajuci se sa sahrane najboljeg
druga, Eugene Colere ga je izbrisao

9
00:01:26,868 --> 00:01:28,870
iz svog adresara.

10
00:01:33,541 --> 00:01:37,211
U istom trenutku,
sperma sa jednim X hromozomom

11
00:01:37,503 --> 00:01:39,755
koja je pripadala Raphaelu Poulainu

12
00:01:40,214 --> 00:01:43,843
pojurila je ka jajetu
njegove zene, Amandine.

13
00:01:44,844 --> 00:01:45,970
9 meseci kasnije,

14
00:01:46,596 --> 00:01:48,222
Amelija Poulain je rodjena.

15
00:01:53,728 --> 00:01:57,440
CUDESNA  SUDBINA
AMELIJE  PULEN

16
00:03:33,286 --> 00:03:35,997
Njen otac, bivsi doktor u vojsci,

17
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:38,249
radi u banji
u Enghien Les Bains.

18
00:03:38,666 --> 00:03:40,501
USKI KUKOVI
TVRDO SRCE

19
00:03:41,294 --> 00:03:43,504
Raphael Poulain ne voli

20
00:03:43,588 --> 00:03:47,508
da urinira pored nekog drugog.
Takodje ne voli

21
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:51,012
da prezrivo gledaju
na njegove sandale,

22
00:03:54,307 --> 00:03:57,476
tesne gacice za kupanje.

23
00:03:59,896 --> 00:04:01,522
Raphael Poulain voli

24
00:04:02,565 --> 00:04:05,026
da odmotava
rolne toalet papira,

25
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:10,239
da redja i cisti svoje cipele,

26
00:04:11,741 --> 00:04:12,658
da prazni svoju
kutiju sa alatom,

27
00:04:13,743 --> 00:04:15,203
da je cisti,

28
00:04:16,245 --> 00:04:18,664
i vraca sve nazad.

29
00:04:19,624 --> 00:04:23,211
Amelijina majka,
uciteljica iz Gurgaona

30
00:04:23,294 --> 00:04:25,004
je oduvek imala slabe nerve.

31
00:04:25,296 --> 00:04:27,173
TIKOVI
SLABI NERVI

32
00:04:27,298 --> 00:04:31,469
Ona ne voli
nabrane prste u kadi,

33
00:04:32,553 --> 00:04:34,805
da joj ruke

34
00:04:34,931 --> 00:04:36,307
diraju stranci,

35
00:04:37,975 --> 00:04:41,229
tragove jastuka
na obrazima izjutra.

36
00:04:41,687 --> 00:04:45,525
Amandine Poulain voli kostime
umetnickih klizaca na TV-u,

37
00:04:46,651 --> 00:04:49,028
poliranje parketa,

38
00:04:49,737 --> 00:04:50,738
da prazni svoju tasnu,

39
00:04:51,322 --> 00:04:52,657
da je cisti,

40
00:04:53,658 --> 00:04:55,701
i da sve vraca nazad.

41
00:04:59,830 --> 00:05:01,582
Amelie ima 6 godina.

42
00:05:01,666 --> 00:05:06,003
Kao i sve devojcice, voli
da je tata grli.

43
00:05:06,087 --> 00:05:10,049
Ali on je nikada ne dodiruje,
osim zbog mesecnog pregleda.

44
00:05:10,174 --> 00:05:12,760
Uzbudjenje zbog retkog dodira

45
00:05:12,844 --> 00:05:15,179
uzrokuje da joj srce lupa.

46
00:05:15,304 --> 00:05:16,681
Kao rezultat toga,

47
00:05:16,764 --> 00:05:19,225
on misli da
ona ima srcanu manu.

48
00:05:20,142 --> 00:05:22,228
Proglasena
nesposobnom za skolu,

49
00:05:23,229 --> 00:05:25,481
Ameliju uci njena majka.

50
00:05:27,108 --> 00:05:27,942
Kokoske

51
00:05:28,025 --> 00:05:29,235
se gaje

52
00:05:29,527 --> 00:05:30,570
ovde

53
00:05:30,695 --> 00:05:32,989
od sada.

54
00:05:33,072 --> 00:05:35,116
4 kokoske gaje...

55
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:36,701
Vrlo dobro.

56
00:05:37,034 --> 00:05:38,578
Od sada!

57
00:05:40,121 --> 00:05:42,165
Lisena drustva,

58
00:05:42,248 --> 00:05:45,668
bacena izmedju neuroze
i ledenog brega,

59
00:05:45,751 --> 00:05:48,754
Amelija se povlaci
u svoju mastu.

60
00:05:50,006 --> 00:05:52,925
U tom svetu,
ploce se prave kao palacinke.

61
00:05:54,010 --> 00:05:56,220
Komsijina zena u komi

62
00:05:56,345 --> 00:06:00,057
je izabrala da se naspava
za ceo zivot odjednom.

63
00:06:00,183 --> 00:06:03,853
Posle ovoga mogu da
da ostanem budna danonocno.

64
00:06:06,856 --> 00:06:09,692
Amelija ima jednog
prijatelja, Placka.

65
00:06:09,775 --> 00:06:14,113
Na nesrecu,uslovi u kuci
su ucinili Placka suicidnim.

66
00:06:32,798 --> 00:06:36,385
Plackovi pokusaji samoubistva
unistavaju majcine nerve.

67
00:06:36,469 --> 00:06:37,970
Odluka je doneta.

68
00:06:38,095 --> 00:06:39,847
Dosta!

69
00:07:13,339 --> 00:07:17,969
Da bi utesila Ameliju, majka
joj daje korisceni "idiot".

70
00:07:30,106 --> 00:07:32,400
Devojcice!
Vidi sta si uradila!

71
00:07:32,525 --> 00:07:37,488
Komsija je zavarava, da
njena kamera izaziva nesrece.

72
00:07:38,739 --> 00:07:42,952
Posto je slikala celo
popodne, Amelija je prestravljena.

73
00:07:43,411 --> 00:07:46,330
Bulji u TV,
pogodjena krivicom

74
00:07:46,414 --> 00:07:48,374
da je izazvala veliki pozar,

75
00:07:48,833 --> 00:07:50,334
dva ispadanja iz sina,

76
00:07:50,751 --> 00:07:52,253
pad dzambo dzeta.

77
00:07:53,337 --> 00:07:54,213
Par dana kasnije,

78
00:07:54,547 --> 00:07:56,090
shvativsi da je prevarena,

79
00:07:56,757 --> 00:07:59,343
Amelija se sveti.

80
00:08:09,812 --> 00:08:10,438
Sta...?

81
00:08:40,301 --> 00:08:42,178
Jednog dana,
nastupa tragedija.

82
00:08:42,261 --> 00:08:44,847
Amandine vodi Ameliju
u Notr Dam

83
00:08:44,931 --> 00:08:47,433
da se mole za mladjeg brata.

84
00:08:47,517 --> 00:08:49,477
Nesto kasnije, nebo salje

85
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:55,191
na zalost, ne decaka,
vec Marguerite, turistu iz Kvebeka,

86
00:08:55,274 --> 00:08:57,151
koja je resila da
okonca sebi zivot.

87
00:09:00,488 --> 00:09:03,157
Amandine umire odmah.

88
00:09:05,326 --> 00:09:10,039
Posle majcine smrti,
Amelija zivi sama sa ocem.

89
00:09:10,164 --> 00:09:14,085
Njegove asocijalne
tendencije rastu.

90
00:09:14,168 --> 00:09:17,505
Opsednut je gradnjom
minijaturnog hrama

91
00:09:17,755 --> 00:09:20,925
za cuvanje
majcinog pepela.

92
00:09:25,930 --> 00:09:29,267
Dani, meseci
i godine prolaze.

93
00:09:33,437 --> 00:09:35,439
U takvom mrtvom svetu,

94
00:09:35,523 --> 00:09:39,485
Amelija voli da sanja da ce
zaraditi dovoljno da ode od kuce.

95
00:09:49,495 --> 00:09:52,498
5 godina kasnije, radi
kao konobarica na Montmartru,

96
00:09:53,374 --> 00:09:54,876
kod Dve Vetrenjace.

97
00:09:56,377 --> 00:09:58,045
29-ti je avgust.

98
00:09:58,171 --> 00:10:01,549
Za 48 sati, njen zivot
ce se zauvek promeniti...

99
00:10:04,343 --> 00:10:06,929
Ali to ona jos ne zna.

100
00:10:07,054 --> 00:10:10,933
Zivi povuceno
medju kolegama i musterijama.

101
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:13,561
Suzanne, vlasnik,

102
00:10:13,811 --> 00:10:16,772
malo sepa,
ali nikad ne prospe pice.

103
00:10:16,898 --> 00:10:19,525
Bivsi jahac bez sedla,
voli atlete

104
00:10:20,234 --> 00:10:22,153
koji kukaju
iz razocaranja.

105
00:10:22,361 --> 00:10:26,199
Ne voli da vidi coveka
ponizenog pred svojom decom.

106
00:10:28,242 --> 00:10:31,412
Georgette, prodavacica
duvana, je hipohondar.

107
00:10:31,537 --> 00:10:34,916
Migrene jednog dana, isijas drugog.

108
00:10:35,041 --> 00:10:38,211
Mrzi reci kao
"plod utrobe. "

109
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:42,423
Gina radi sa Amelijom.
Njena baka je bila vidar.

110
00:10:42,924 --> 00:10:45,426
Voli da lomi prste.

111
00:10:45,927 --> 00:10:49,055
Donosi jelo Hipolitu,
propalom piscu.

112
00:10:49,263 --> 00:10:52,517
On voli da gleda kako
toreadore probadaju na TV-u.

113
00:10:55,102 --> 00:10:59,273
Na njih mrko gleda Joseph,
Ginin bisi ljubavnik.

114
00:10:59,357 --> 00:11:01,943
Uvek je ljubomorno prati.

115
00:11:02,068 --> 00:11:03,486
Sve sto on voli je

116
00:11:03,861 --> 00:11:06,322
pucanje balona na kesama.

117
00:11:06,906 --> 00:11:09,200
Evo Philomene, stjuardese.

118
00:11:09,283 --> 00:11:11,911
Amelija joj cuva macku
dok nije tu.

119
00:11:11,994 --> 00:11:13,037
Philomena voli

120
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:15,957
odzvanjanje posude za
macke na plocicama.

121
00:11:16,582 --> 00:11:20,002
Macka voli da prisluskuje
decje price.

122
00:11:21,629 --> 00:11:24,590
Ne hvala g-djo.
Ne radim nedeljom.

123
00:11:25,132 --> 00:11:29,512
Vikendom, Amelija cesto
ide vozom da poseti oca.

124
00:11:30,263 --> 00:11:33,808
-Zasto ne odes u penziju?
-I sta da radim?

125
00:11:33,933 --> 00:11:36,519
Putuj. 
Nikada nisi nigde otisao.

126
00:11:37,603 --> 00:11:42,358
Kada smo bili mladi, majka
i ja smo zeleli da putujemo.

127
00:11:43,025 --> 00:11:46,445
Nismo mogli.
Zbog tvog srca.

128
00:11:46,529 --> 00:11:47,905
Znam.

129
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:49,532
Zato sada

130
00:11:50,658 --> 00:11:51,617
Sada...

131
00:11:52,785 --> 00:11:55,371
Ponekad petkom,
Amelija ide u bioskop.

132
00:11:55,496 --> 00:11:59,709
Volim da gledam
ljudska lica u tami.

133
00:12:06,132 --> 00:12:10,052
Volim da pimecujem detalje
koje niko drugi ne vidi.

134
00:12:12,430 --> 00:12:16,726
Ali mrzim, kad u starim filmovima
vozaci ne gledaju kuda voze.

135
00:12:22,190 --> 00:12:23,733
Amelija nema decka.

136
00:12:24,108 --> 00:12:28,112
Pokusala je par puta,
ali bilo je razocaravajuce.

137
00:12:29,030 --> 00:12:32,742
Umesto toga,ona gaji
ukus za  mala zadovoljstva.

138
00:12:33,534 --> 00:12:35,536
Umakanje ruke u dzak zita,

139
00:12:37,038 --> 00:12:38,414
Lomljenje creme brulee-a

140
00:12:38,539 --> 00:12:40,708
kasicicom.

141
00:12:44,545 --> 00:12:48,257
I bacanje zabica
kod St. Martinovog Kanala.

142
00:13:28,798 --> 00:13:30,967
Zovu ga Stakleni Covek.

143
00:13:31,092 --> 00:13:34,637
Rodjen je sa kostima
lomljivim kao kristal.

144
00:13:34,804 --> 00:13:37,181
Sav namestaj
mu je tapaciran.

145
00:13:37,807 --> 00:13:40,601
Rukovanje bi
mu slomilo prste.

146
00:13:40,810 --> 00:13:42,728
Nije izlazio 20 godina.

147
00:13:47,358 --> 00:13:49,151
Vreme nista nije promenilo.

148
00:13:49,235 --> 00:13:51,654
Amelija jos
uvek trazi samocu.

149
00:13:51,737 --> 00:13:53,656
Zabavlja se
blesavim pitanjima

150
00:13:53,739 --> 00:13:56,242
u vezi sveta,

151
00:13:56,367 --> 00:14:00,079
kao sto je, "Koliko parova
upravo dozivljava orgazam?"

152
00:14:11,215 --> 00:14:12,383
15!

153
00:14:14,802 --> 00:14:17,638
Konacno, 30-tog avgusta 1997.

154
00:14:17,722 --> 00:14:21,976
desava se nesto
sto joj zauvek menja zivot.

155
00:14:22,310 --> 00:14:26,314
Lady Di, Princeza od Velsa,
poginula je u saobracajki

156
00:14:26,814 --> 00:14:30,735
sa svojim pratiocem,
Dodi Al-Fayedom...

157
00:15:22,286 --> 00:15:24,288
Samo bi pronalazac
Tutankamonove grobnice,

158
00:15:24,372 --> 00:15:27,375
znao kako se osecala

159
00:15:28,125 --> 00:15:30,419
po otkricu ovog blaga,

160
00:15:30,503 --> 00:15:33,840
koju je sakrio
neki decak pre 40 godina.

161
00:15:39,554 --> 00:15:42,306
31-og avgusta u 4 ujutru,

162
00:15:42,431 --> 00:15:45,017
Amelija dobija sjajnu ideju.

163
00:15:45,142 --> 00:15:48,855
Ma gde bio,ona ce
naci vlasnika kutije

164
00:15:48,980 --> 00:15:51,023
i vratiti mu njegovo blago.

165
00:15:51,148 --> 00:15:55,987
Ako bi mu to nesto znacilo,
postala bi dobrica za stalno.

166
00:15:56,070 --> 00:15:58,030
A ako ne, bas steta.

167
00:16:04,954 --> 00:16:08,875
Devojka sa 5-tog sprata.
Ne vidjamo te cesto.

168
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:13,004
Da li znas decaka, koji
je ziveo u mom stanu 50-tih?

169
00:16:13,087 --> 00:16:15,089
Decak? Uzmi pice.

170
00:16:17,091 --> 00:16:20,011
-Ne hvala.
-Udji! Zatvori vrata.

171
00:16:20,887 --> 00:16:24,015
Decaci? Znala sam ih mnogo.

172
00:16:24,140 --> 00:16:28,769
Slatki su  dok ne otkriju
grudve i kestenje.

173
00:16:28,895 --> 00:16:30,605
Znala sam mnogo decaka.

174
00:16:30,730 --> 00:16:32,857
Kada si dosla ovde...

175
00:16:32,940 --> 00:16:34,025
94-te.

176
00:16:34,984 --> 00:16:36,819
Mora da si cula pricu.

177
00:16:37,153 --> 00:16:38,696
Ne...

178
00:16:39,572 --> 00:16:40,907
Iznenadjena sam. Sedi.

179
00:16:42,825 --> 00:16:45,661
Moj muz je radio
za osiguravajucu firmu.

180
00:16:46,162 --> 00:16:49,290
Nije tajna, da me je
varao sa svojom sekretaricom.

181
00:16:51,167 --> 00:16:53,294
Koristili su sve
hotele u blizini.

182
00:16:53,836 --> 00:16:55,087
I to ne jeftine.

183
00:16:55,338 --> 00:16:58,299
Drolja je volela da siri noge

184
00:16:59,091 --> 00:17:00,009
ali samo na satenu.

185
00:17:01,302 --> 00:17:03,054
Zato je uzimao
novac iz kase.

186
00:17:03,346 --> 00:17:06,098
U pocetku malo,
a onda 50 miliona.

187
00:17:07,350 --> 00:17:09,310
Odleteli su za Panamu.

188
00:17:11,896 --> 00:17:12,772
Popij!

189
00:17:14,857 --> 00:17:17,610
20-tog januara 1970-te

190
00:17:18,194 --> 00:17:20,238
zazvonili su mi na vratima.

191
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:25,243
"Muz vam je poginuo u
saobracajki u Juznoj Americi."

192
00:17:27,203 --> 00:17:28,538
Tu je moj zivot stao.

193
00:17:28,913 --> 00:17:31,749
Crni lav je umro
od tuge.

194
00:17:34,252 --> 00:17:35,837
Jadno stvorenje!

195
00:17:38,130 --> 00:17:41,259
Vidis li kako sa ljubavlju
gleda u svog gospodara?

196
00:17:43,803 --> 00:17:45,054
Procitacu ti njegova pisma.

197
00:17:45,388 --> 00:17:46,931
Ne idi!

198
00:17:47,014 --> 00:17:48,891
Imas valjda 5 minuta.

199
00:17:50,393 --> 00:17:52,728
Ovo je pisao
iz vojnog kampa.

200
00:17:55,648 --> 00:17:56,816
"Draga Mado"

201
00:17:57,024 --> 00:17:58,818
To sam ja Madeleine.

202
00:17:58,901 --> 00:18:01,696
"Ne mogu ni da jedem
ni da spavam.

203
00:18:01,821 --> 00:18:06,576
"zato sto je smisao
mog zivota daleko u Parizu.

204
00:18:07,076 --> 00:18:10,329
"i necu je videti do
sledeceg petka,

205
00:18:10,413 --> 00:18:14,709
"kada ce se moja slatka
lasica pojaviti na stanici

206
00:18:15,376 --> 00:18:18,087
"u plavoj haljini..."

207
00:18:18,212 --> 00:18:22,133
u zagradi "ona na koju mislis
da je previse providna."

208
00:18:30,725 --> 00:18:32,810
Je li tebi iko tako pisao?

209
00:18:34,020 --> 00:18:36,689
Ja nisam nicija mala lasica.

210
00:18:38,149 --> 00:18:39,400
Zovem se Madeleine Wells.

211
00:18:40,234 --> 00:18:42,695
Madeleine, kao
Marija Magdalena.

212
00:18:43,404 --> 00:18:45,740
Plakala je?

213
00:18:54,749 --> 00:18:56,000
U vezi tvog pitanja...

214
00:18:57,084 --> 00:19:01,422
Pitaj prodavca Collignona.
Celog zivota zivi ovde.

215
00:19:03,174 --> 00:19:04,884
Zdravo Amelijo-slatka!

216
00:19:05,218 --> 00:19:07,386
Smokvu i tri
oraha kao i obicno?

217
00:19:07,887 --> 00:19:10,348
Ko je ziveo u
mom stanu 50-tih?

218
00:19:10,431 --> 00:19:12,433
Kako su se zvali?

219
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:14,602
Nemam pojma
draga moja.

220
00:19:14,685 --> 00:19:18,814
1950-te imao sam 2 godine.
Mentalni uzrast kretena.

221
00:19:18,940 --> 00:19:20,274
"Kreten" je Lucien.

222
00:19:20,358 --> 00:19:24,111
Nije genije, ali Ameliji se
dopada. Dopada joj se

223
00:19:24,237 --> 00:19:27,365
kako se brine o svakoj
zucanici, kao da je dragocenost

224
00:19:27,615 --> 00:19:30,743
koju treba cuvati.
Tako on pokazuje

225
00:19:30,868 --> 00:19:32,286
da voli dobro
obavljen posao.

226
00:19:32,411 --> 00:19:33,788
Vidi ga samo!

227
00:19:33,871 --> 00:19:36,916
Kao da neguje pticicu!

228
00:19:37,917 --> 00:19:40,628
Ne trazi mu ribizle.

229
00:19:40,753 --> 00:19:42,129
Vrati se
do ponedeljka!

230
00:19:43,673 --> 00:19:45,299
Mrdaj ukoceni!

231
00:19:46,133 --> 00:19:47,385
Nema ceo dan!

232
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:56,269
Poseti moju majku.
Ima slonovsko pamcenje.

233
00:19:56,394 --> 00:19:57,854
Mama slon!

234
00:19:59,856 --> 00:20:00,940
Hvala.

235
00:20:19,834 --> 00:20:20,960
Bredoteau.

236
00:20:24,172 --> 00:20:25,631
Ima koje trazis.

237
00:20:25,715 --> 00:20:30,136
Ali ako ja to kazem ne vazi.
Senilan sam.

238
00:20:30,219 --> 00:20:32,138
Ignorisi ga, on je senilan.

239
00:20:33,097 --> 00:20:35,057
Vidi sta mi je
uradio sa lovorom?

240
00:20:39,520 --> 00:20:41,856
Poslednji posao mu je bio
ponistavanje karti u metrou.

241
00:20:42,231 --> 00:20:44,859
Sada ustaje svake noci

242
00:20:45,484 --> 00:20:47,904
da busi rupe u mom lovoru!

243
00:20:48,029 --> 00:20:50,489
Steta sto to nije tesko.

244
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:54,202
Svako mora da se
nekako opusti.

245
00:20:54,285 --> 00:20:55,244
Ja bacam kamencice.

246
00:20:55,453 --> 00:20:57,747
-Stvarno?
-Nacicu ne brini.

247
00:20:58,080 --> 00:20:59,373
Vrlo sam organizovana.

248
00:20:59,749 --> 00:21:01,375
-Sve mi se dopada.
-Kao sta?

249
00:21:02,543 --> 00:21:05,421
Tvoj sin ima skoro 50,
a ja mu jos uvek vodim

250
00:21:05,546 --> 00:21:07,256
knjigovodstvo!

251
00:21:07,381 --> 00:21:11,010
Stavljala si mu pastu za zube
kad je imao 15 godina.

252
00:21:11,093 --> 00:21:12,094
Sledi.

253
00:21:13,429 --> 00:21:14,388
Camus...

254
00:21:14,472 --> 00:21:18,351
2-gi sprat, Brossard
je bio u B bloku...

255
00:21:18,809 --> 00:21:19,977
Evo ga!

256
00:21:20,478 --> 00:21:22,063
Bredoteau. 5-ti sprat.

257
00:21:23,439 --> 00:21:25,233
Bili su severnjaci.

258
00:21:25,316 --> 00:21:26,901
Bredoteau.

259
00:21:27,276 --> 00:21:28,694
Sta vise da kazem?

260
00:21:32,281 --> 00:21:37,119
...kako da zivim?

261
00:21:37,495 --> 00:21:46,921
Da nikad ne upoznam
srecu koju pruzas

262
00:21:47,004 --> 00:21:51,175
Kada sam ti u zagrljaju

263
00:21:51,509 --> 00:21:56,973
U tvojoj sam moci

264
00:21:57,765 --> 00:22:03,980
Kako da zivim

265
00:22:05,314 --> 00:22:10,444
bez tebe?

266
00:22:32,508 --> 00:22:35,970
Onaj sto pipa ispod kabine
za snimanje je Nino Quincampoix.

267
00:22:40,516 --> 00:22:45,188
Kada Ameliji ponestane drustva,
Nino ga ima previse.

268
00:22:56,991 --> 00:22:59,452
5 milja odvojeni,
oboje su sanjali

269
00:22:59,577 --> 00:23:01,412
da imaju brata ili sestru,

270
00:23:01,579 --> 00:23:04,040
sa kojima bi stalno bili.

271
00:23:25,186 --> 00:23:26,729
Zdravo tata.

272
00:23:27,939 --> 00:23:29,857
Novi prijatelj?

273
00:23:30,316 --> 00:23:32,401
Imam ga godinama.

274
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:37,031
Tvoja majka ga je
mrzela, pa je ziveo u supi.

275
00:23:37,114 --> 00:23:39,367
Hajde da ih pomirimo.

276
00:23:44,205 --> 00:23:45,498
Sta kazes na to?

277
00:23:49,001 --> 00:23:54,340
Tata, kada bi nasao relikviju
iz svog detinjstva

278
00:23:54,465 --> 00:23:58,511
kako bi se osecao?
Srecno? Tuzno? Nostalgicno?

279
00:23:59,303 --> 00:24:01,889
Ovaj patuljak nije relikvija.

280
00:24:01,973 --> 00:24:05,434
Bio je oprostajni poklon
od mog starog puka.

281
00:24:05,977 --> 00:24:10,439
Ne, mislim nesto sto si
sakrio kao tajno blago.

282
00:24:11,566 --> 00:24:14,402
Trebalo bi da ga
izlakiram pre jeseni.

283
00:24:17,488 --> 00:24:20,074
Skuvacu caj. Hoces i ti?

284
00:24:20,158 --> 00:24:23,244
Udahni, ne mrdaj.

285
00:24:24,328 --> 00:24:26,247
Bolje?

286
00:24:26,330 --> 00:24:27,832
Zatvori vrata!

287
00:24:28,499 --> 00:24:29,917
Besni oluja!

288
00:24:30,501 --> 00:24:31,961
Nije ovo Sibir.

289
00:24:32,503 --> 00:24:35,923
Nisi alergicna na
izduvne gasove!

290
00:24:36,007 --> 00:24:39,385
Skoro sam iskasljala
plucnu maramicu sinoc.

291
00:24:39,510 --> 00:24:41,095
Iskasljala plucnu maramicu?

292
00:24:41,179 --> 00:24:44,223
-Sta ima danas Suzanne?
-Zucanica au gratin.

293
00:24:44,932 --> 00:24:47,059
Bices na kolenima.

294
00:24:47,185 --> 00:24:47,977
To je dobro?

295
00:24:48,060 --> 00:24:50,813
-Zavisi gde padnes.
-Ispred toaleta...

296
00:24:50,897 --> 00:24:51,939
Ne valja!

297
00:24:57,528 --> 00:25:01,324
12:15: smeje se orgazmicno
da privuce alfa muzjaka.

298
00:25:02,325 --> 00:25:04,285
Izludece me.

299
00:25:05,036 --> 00:25:08,080
Zasto ne odustane?
Ima toliko drugih kafica!

300
00:25:10,374 --> 00:25:11,417
Suzanne?

301
00:25:13,503 --> 00:25:16,005
"Au gratin" znaci
u sosu, jel' tako?

302
00:25:17,089 --> 00:25:17,757
Da. Zasto?

303
00:25:18,382 --> 00:25:22,929
Ne mogu da to podnesem.
Kao ni ti konjetinu.

304
00:25:23,054 --> 00:25:26,265
Ne moj zeludac,
vec moje secanje.

305
00:25:26,933 --> 00:25:28,476
Radije bih skuvala coveka.

306
00:25:29,352 --> 00:25:30,520
Salis se!

307
00:25:44,283 --> 00:25:46,118
Mogu li  danas
da odem ranije?

308
00:25:47,245 --> 00:25:48,162
Kako se zove?

309
00:25:48,955 --> 00:25:50,873
Dominique Bredoteau.

310
00:25:59,924 --> 00:26:00,925
Vi ste Dominique Bredoteau?

311
00:26:01,425 --> 00:26:02,385
Ja sam.

312
00:26:03,302 --> 00:26:04,887
Zasto?

313
00:26:05,888 --> 00:26:06,931
To je zbog...

314
00:26:07,932 --> 00:26:08,891
peticije.

315
00:26:09,392 --> 00:26:10,268
Peticije?

316
00:26:12,103 --> 00:26:14,981
Peticije za...

317
00:26:17,108 --> 00:26:18,276
posvetu Lady Di!

318
00:26:18,985 --> 00:26:19,986
Ne hvala.

319
00:26:29,203 --> 00:26:31,664
Dame i gospodo
izvinite na smetnji...

320
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,840
trazim
Dominique Bredoteaua.

321
00:26:40,923 --> 00:26:43,801
Za Evropski cenzus.

322
00:26:43,885 --> 00:26:46,345
Dodjite. Treci sprat.

323
00:26:56,022 --> 00:26:57,648
Cao mace.

324
00:27:00,401 --> 00:27:01,777
Caj Earl Grey?

325
00:27:01,861 --> 00:27:03,738
Od jasmina?

326
00:27:05,072 --> 00:27:06,866
Sta cete?

327
00:27:10,912 --> 00:27:12,079
Zauzeta sam.

328
00:27:22,882 --> 00:27:24,008
Stizem!

329
00:27:24,133 --> 00:27:27,845
Gde mogu da nadjem
Dominique Bredoteaua?

330
00:27:29,180 --> 00:27:33,267
Bas steta!
Upravo je otisao.

331
00:27:33,935 --> 00:27:36,896
Evo ga, odlazi.

332
00:27:46,280 --> 00:27:47,031
Bretodeau.

333
00:27:48,866 --> 00:27:49,951
Ne Bredoteau.

334
00:27:52,078 --> 00:27:55,456
Treba ti malo slatkog vina.

335
00:27:55,748 --> 00:27:56,833
Udji.

336
00:28:01,921 --> 00:28:05,299
Zivim ovde 5 godina.
Nisam vas vidjala ranije.

337
00:28:06,384 --> 00:28:09,136
Nikad ne izlazim na odmoriste.

338
00:28:09,220 --> 00:28:12,765
Izbirljiv sam, sa
kim se upoznajem.

339
00:28:13,307 --> 00:28:15,309
Sve su to propalice.

340
00:28:17,019 --> 00:28:18,938
Udji.

341
00:28:22,066 --> 00:28:24,861
Zovu me Stakleni Covek

342
00:28:25,027 --> 00:28:28,781
ali ime mi je Raymond Dufayel.

343
00:28:29,907 --> 00:28:33,953
-Amelija Pulen. Konobarica sam...
-Kod Dve Vetrenjace. Znam.

344
00:28:34,912 --> 00:28:40,459
I sada je tvoja
Bredoteau korpa je prazna.

345
00:28:41,502 --> 00:28:44,797
Zsto sto nije "ovo" onda je "to."

346
00:28:45,006 --> 00:28:46,757
Kao "Toto".

347
00:28:51,345 --> 00:28:52,763
Volim tu sliku.

348
00:28:53,431 --> 00:28:56,267
Kao svecani rucak
Brodske Zabave.

349
00:28:57,852 --> 00:28:58,686
Od Renoira.

350
00:29:04,358 --> 00:29:08,279
Slikam jednu godisnje,
zadnjih 20 godina.

351
00:29:10,698 --> 00:29:12,700
Najtezi deo je izgled.

352
00:29:13,242 --> 00:29:14,827
Ponekad se
osecam kao da

353
00:29:14,952 --> 00:29:18,289
namerno menjaju
raspolozenje meni iza ledja.

354
00:29:19,248 --> 00:29:21,000
Izgledaju prilicno srecno.

355
00:29:21,083 --> 00:29:22,627
I trebalo bi!

356
00:29:23,044 --> 00:29:25,796
Jedu zacinjenu zecetinu

357
00:29:26,255 --> 00:29:29,717
i palacinke sa
dzemom za decu.

358
00:29:31,177 --> 00:29:36,140
Gde je onaj papir?

359
00:29:37,892 --> 00:29:42,021
Primecujes moju kameru.

360
00:29:43,064 --> 00:29:45,441
Poklon od snaje.

361
00:29:46,025 --> 00:29:48,361
Stavljam je tu

362
00:29:48,945 --> 00:29:52,240
da ne bih navijao satove.

363
00:29:53,115 --> 00:29:55,868
Posle svih ovih godina

364
00:29:55,952 --> 00:30:00,206
jedina osoba koju jos
uvek ne mogu da uhvatim

365
00:30:00,289 --> 00:30:03,209
je devojka sa casom vode.

366
00:30:04,001 --> 00:30:06,712
Ona je u sredini, a opet izvan.

367
00:30:08,339 --> 00:30:11,133
Mozda je prosto drugacija.

368
00:30:12,343 --> 00:30:14,136
Na koji nacin?

369
00:30:15,429 --> 00:30:16,848
Ne znam.

370
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:23,104
Kada je bila mala, retko
se igrala sa ostalom  decom.

371
00:30:24,188 --> 00:30:26,190
Mozda nikada.

372
00:30:31,362 --> 00:30:35,950
Dominique Bretodeau
27 Rue Mouffetard.

373
00:30:37,493 --> 00:30:38,953
Ovo je za tebe.

374
00:30:39,495 --> 00:30:41,455
Svakog utorka ujutru,

375
00:30:41,539 --> 00:30:44,292
Dominique Bretodeau
kupuje piletinu.

376
00:30:44,375 --> 00:30:47,295
Pece je  sa krompirom.

377
00:30:48,171 --> 00:30:50,464
Posto odreze batake i krila

378
00:30:51,048 --> 00:30:54,886
voli da opipava toplo
telo svojim prstima,

379
00:30:55,136 --> 00:30:57,346
pocevsi od skoljki.

380
00:31:00,224 --> 00:31:03,895
Ali ne danas.
Bretodeau nece kupiti piletinu.

381
00:31:04,020 --> 00:31:07,773
Nece stici dalje
od govornice, ove.

382
00:32:17,134 --> 00:32:20,263
U trenu, vratice se.

383
00:32:21,013 --> 00:32:23,349
Bahamontes kako osvaja
Tur de Frans.

384
00:32:26,978 --> 00:32:29,105
Tetka Josetteini kombinezoni...

385
00:32:31,315 --> 00:32:33,943
i najvise, tragicni dan...

386
00:32:36,821 --> 00:32:39,240
dan, kada je
osvojio sve klikere.

387
00:33:01,095 --> 00:33:03,347
Prikljesteni Bretodeau!

388
00:33:13,191 --> 00:33:14,817
Konjak molim.

389
00:33:20,490 --> 00:33:22,366
Zadivljujuce je, sta
se upravo desilo.

390
00:33:23,034 --> 00:33:25,369
Mora da je
moj andjeo cuvar.

391
00:33:27,371 --> 00:33:29,165
Govornica me je zvala...

392
00:33:34,337 --> 00:33:37,548
I mene isto!
Zvala me je mikrotalasna.

393
00:33:40,343 --> 00:33:42,178
Jos jedan konjak.

394
00:33:51,395 --> 00:33:53,231
Bas je zivot cudan.

395
00:33:54,857 --> 00:33:59,278
Detetu vreme sporo prolazi.
Onda imas odjednom 50.

396
00:34:03,074 --> 00:34:07,370
Sve sto ti je ostalo od
detinjstva stane u zardjalu kutiju.

397
00:34:11,249 --> 00:34:13,334
Imate li dece g-djice?

398
00:34:17,839 --> 00:34:20,383
Imam cerku vasih godina.

399
00:34:24,136 --> 00:34:26,764
Nismo se culi godinama.

400
00:34:27,306 --> 00:34:30,935
Cuo sam da je dobila sina.

401
00:34:31,435 --> 00:34:33,354
Zove se Lucas.

402
00:34:39,151 --> 00:34:43,406
Vreme je da ih nadjem, pre
nego sto i ja zavrsim u kutiji.

403
00:34:45,074 --> 00:34:46,409
Ne mislis tako?

404
00:34:54,458 --> 00:34:58,462
Amelija je odjednom dobila
osecaj potpune harmonije.

405
00:34:58,588 --> 00:35:01,424
Savrseni trenutak.
 Blago osvetljenje,

406
00:35:01,507 --> 00:35:05,469
miris u  vazduhu,
tihi zagor ulice...

407
00:35:05,553 --> 00:35:08,973
Udise duboko.
Zivot je jednostavan i lak.

408
00:35:09,056 --> 00:35:13,394
Talas ljubavi, potreba
da pomogne covecanstvu je obuzima.

409
00:35:26,407 --> 00:35:29,994
Da vam pomognem.
Sidjite. Eto nas!

410
00:35:30,077 --> 00:35:31,579
Udovica tambur-majora!

411
00:35:31,871 --> 00:35:34,957
Nosi njegov kaput
od kada je umro.

412
00:35:35,374 --> 00:35:37,960
Konjskoj glavi fali uvo!

413
00:35:38,044 --> 00:35:41,380
Cvecar se smeje.
Ima naborane oci.

414
00:35:42,173 --> 00:35:44,425
Lizalice u izlogu pekare!

415
00:35:45,426 --> 00:35:46,344
Pomirisi to!

416
00:35:46,427 --> 00:35:49,305
Dele parcice dinje.

417
00:35:50,598 --> 00:35:52,850
Sladoled od sljiva!

418
00:35:53,434 --> 00:35:55,478
Prolazimo pored kasapnice.

419
00:35:55,561 --> 00:35:58,022
Sunka 79 franaka.
Rebra 45!

420
00:35:58,439 --> 00:36:02,902
Sada prodavnica sira.
Picador je 12.90. Cabecaus 23.

421
00:36:03,402 --> 00:36:07,156
Beba gleda psa
koji osmatra kokoske!

422
00:36:07,865 --> 00:36:10,993
Sada smo kod
kioska ispred metroa.

423
00:36:11,077 --> 00:36:13,204
Ostavicu vas ovde. Cao!

424
00:37:04,672 --> 00:37:07,925
"Ne moze da razume druge."

425
00:37:09,260 --> 00:37:11,888
"Uvek je bila usamljeno dete."

426
00:37:14,932 --> 00:37:17,935
U iskricavo
popodne u julu,

427
00:37:18,019 --> 00:37:20,813
dok su se na plazama,
horde turista

428
00:37:20,897 --> 00:37:23,357
odmarale na novom suncu

429
00:37:23,441 --> 00:37:26,110
a Parizani okupani u znoju

430
00:37:26,194 --> 00:37:28,321
gledali u eksplozije

431
00:37:28,446 --> 00:37:30,323
tradicionalnog vatrometa,

432
00:37:30,448 --> 00:37:31,949
Amelija Pulen,

433
00:37:32,033 --> 00:37:37,246
Kuma izgnanika,
Bogorodica nevoljenih,

434
00:37:37,371 --> 00:37:39,457
je konacno podlegla umoru.

435
00:37:40,625 --> 00:37:44,337
Na obolelim ulicama Pariza,

436
00:37:44,462 --> 00:37:47,423
gomile ozaloscenih

437
00:37:47,548 --> 00:37:50,426
su se tiho poredjale
u pogrebnu povorku

438
00:37:51,093 --> 00:37:55,473
sa neizrecivom tugom
novonastalih sirocadi.

439
00:37:56,098 --> 00:37:58,142
Kakva neobicna sudbina
za nekoga,

440
00:37:58,559 --> 00:38:00,394
koji je pruzao sve,

441
00:38:00,478 --> 00:38:04,565
a opet uzivao samo u
malim zivotnim zadovoljstvima.

442
00:38:05,566 --> 00:38:08,986
Kao Don Kihot,
borila se za druge

443
00:38:09,070 --> 00:38:13,282
pod zvrnjem svih
zivotnih nedaca.

444
00:38:24,585 --> 00:38:26,546
Bila je to
izgubljena bitka

445
00:38:26,838 --> 00:38:31,300
koja joj je prerano uzela zivot.
Sa jedva 23, Amelija Pulen

446
00:38:31,425 --> 00:38:34,887
je dopustila da joj se
umorno telo spoji,

447
00:38:35,012 --> 00:38:38,140
padom i tokom
univerzalnog jada.

448
00:38:39,934 --> 00:38:44,397
Dok je odlazila, osetila je kamen
kajanja sto je pustila oca da umre,

449
00:38:44,939 --> 00:38:49,193
a da ne pokusa, da
u njegov ugusen zivot

450
00:38:49,277 --> 00:38:52,363
udahne malo vazduha
koji je dala

451
00:38:52,905 --> 00:38:54,574
mnogim drugima.

452
00:41:10,751 --> 00:41:12,003
Stanite!

453
00:42:11,604 --> 00:42:13,356
Stranice pune
fotografija za dokumenta,

454
00:42:13,439 --> 00:42:17,068
iscepane i odbacene
od svojih vlasnika,

455
00:42:17,193 --> 00:42:20,446
koje je pazljivo
sastavio neki cudak.

456
00:42:22,198 --> 00:42:24,283
Kakav porodican album!

457
00:42:28,329 --> 00:42:29,455
Paklu Goloaza.

458
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:32,917
Samo trenutak.
Ovde je tako zadimljeno!

459
00:42:33,042 --> 00:42:35,461
Gde su?
Nista ne vidim.

460
00:42:35,586 --> 00:42:38,130
Vise levo. Vise...

461
00:42:42,218 --> 00:42:43,177
Treba ti promena...

462
00:42:44,428 --> 00:42:45,555
Zaboravi.

463
