4:08.

999
01:47:39,157 --> 01:47:42,785
On se vrati i eto!
Odose zajedno.

1000
01:47:47,039 --> 01:47:50,084
Brinem se za Ameliju,
zato sto mi se svidjas.

1001
01:47:50,168 --> 01:47:51,419
Kako to mislis?

1002
01:47:51,502 --> 01:47:55,339
Uopste, ljudi koji mi
se dopadaju nisu normalni.

1003
01:47:55,465 --> 01:47:58,426
-Zelim da znam vise o tebi.
-Pitaj me.

1004
01:48:01,345 --> 01:48:03,139
Jedna lasta ne cini?

1005
01:48:04,140 --> 01:48:05,391
Lasta?

1006
01:48:06,851 --> 01:48:08,227
Prolece.

1007
01:48:08,352 --> 01:48:09,729
Vezbanje vodi ka...

1008
01:48:09,854 --> 01:48:11,147
Savrsenstvu.

1009
01:48:11,355 --> 01:48:12,815
-Ne turaj nos...
-Gde ne treba.

1010
01:48:12,899 --> 01:48:14,317
-Sto je brzo...
-To je kuso.

1011
01:48:14,442 --> 01:48:16,194
-Rolling stone...
-Gathers no moss.

1012
01:48:16,319 --> 01:48:18,321
-Greh je krasti...
-Jer ces nisko pasti.

1013
01:48:18,446 --> 01:48:22,033
-Daleko od ociju...
-Daleko od srca.

1014
01:48:22,158 --> 01:48:23,826
-Nije lose.
-Sakupljas ih?

1015
01:48:24,494 --> 01:48:28,664
U mom kraju kazu, da
ko zna izreke nije toliko los.

1016
01:48:32,835 --> 01:48:36,380
Lepa devojko sa 5-tog
sprata, cuj ovo!

1017
01:48:36,506 --> 01:48:39,717
-Verujes u cuda?
-Ne danas.

1018
01:48:40,885 --> 01:48:42,929
Ceka te iznenadjenje.

1019
01:48:43,095 --> 01:48:46,808
Sta ako ti kazem,
da je tim planinara

1020
01:48:46,933 --> 01:48:50,353
na Mont Blanu nasao

1021
01:48:50,478 --> 01:48:55,316
cvrsti dokaz da
me je muz voleo?

1022
01:49:28,182 --> 01:49:30,434
Lucien, treba mi kvasac.

1023
01:49:30,518 --> 01:49:34,397
Za g-djicu Ameliju?
Sprema svoj cuveni kolac sa sljivama?

1024
01:51:04,654 --> 01:51:06,614
Vraticu se.

1025
01:51:36,602 --> 01:51:39,564
Udjite u spavacu sobu,
g-djice Poulain.

1026
01:51:55,663 --> 01:51:58,624
Pa, mala Amelija,

1027
01:52:00,001 --> 01:52:02,879
vase kosti nisu od stakla.

1028
01:52:03,004 --> 01:52:06,048
Mozete da izdrzite
udarce zivota.

1029
01:52:06,507 --> 01:52:10,428
Ako pustite da
vam sanse izmicu,

1030
01:52:11,679 --> 01:52:17,185
vremenom, srce
ce vam postati

1031
01:52:17,310 --> 01:52:22,482
suvo i lomljivo
kao moj kostur.

1032
01:52:24,984 --> 01:52:26,027
Pa...

1033
01:52:26,819 --> 01:52:29,822
Krenite za njim,
za ime Boga!

